          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "G.Kessedjian (2010-11-10)",
                " If one want to write the covariance matrix of these",
                " data for the generalized least-squares calculations,",
                " the fission probability covariance matrix and the",
                " calculated compound nucleus cross section covariance",
                " matrix are needed. For the first one, we can show that",
                " the covariance is the product of systematic errors.",
                " For the second one, it is not true. As a consequence,",
                " the covariance matrix determination of these data is",
                " not so obvious."
              ]
            }
